Robber- (4)
- Has the ability to check any individual player's or any team's vault/wallet balance every night. (Similar to the market item)
- The person/team who was/were robbed or checked will not be informed the first time it happens, but will be informed of the same every time after.
- They can also conduct a robbery, stealing 20% of the vault's/wallet's balance. This ability has a cooldown of 2 phases and is used instead of the regular check.
- The robber picks the target (Either a Person or a Team) and an action during the night. The robber gets the money when the night comes to an end. 
- Respawns in 4 phases.
